              <title>Discussion: Project evaluation</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2662</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2662</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>During the sessions with Alison Muirhead and Helen Beetham at the Cluster's November CAMEL meeting, some key challenges in evaluating the impact of the projects were identified. (See also Grainne's notes from the session with Alison <a href="/cloud/view/2650">here</a>). Broadly these questions were asked:</p>
