<li>How might we evaluate the <em>quality</em> of designs? What criteria are we using?&nbsp; Are they the same across the projects? </li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>What do we mean by the terms '<em>sharing</em>' or '<em>community</em>'? Do we mean the same things? How do we evaluate and document change in these?</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>How will we capture the impact of the 'principles' on practice? How can we be 'sure enough' that the changes we discover are as a result of the interventions we make?</li>
</ul>]]></description>
